    <fr:title text="Matrix product is relational composition › "><fr:link href="jms-00J2.xml" title="Matrix product is relational composition" addr="jms-00J2" type="local"><fr:link href="jms-00IV.xml" title="Product of matrices" addr="jms-00IV" type="local">Matrix product</fr:link> is <fr:link href="jms-00IN.xml" title="Relational composite" addr="jms-00IN" type="local">relational composition</fr:link></fr:link> › </fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>We use the fact that the additive operation of the boolean semiring is disjunction and the multiplicative operation is conjunction:</fr:p>

 <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
   {\mathopen {}\left (N\cdot  M\right )\mathclose {}}_{i,j} &= \bigoplus _{k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}} M_{i,k}\cdot  N_{k,j}
   \\
   &=
   \bigvee _{k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}} M_{i,k}\land  N_{k,j}
   \\
   &=
   \exists  k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}\mathpunct {.}
   M_{i,k}\land  N_{k,j}
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter>
